{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>ViuTV年度音樂盛事《CHILL CLUB推介榜 年度推介25/26》今晚（5月3日）盛大舉行。許志安驚喜現身擔任表演嘉賓，先與MIRROR成員AK（江𤒹生）合唱《翻騰》。許志安着閃片外套和戴帽，型爆跳唱，型仔程度不輸AK。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127713117166374912169534.jpeg/jjJ_7l09N7VDexi8UsVAnvxZSB08-xUy9Xor1Nx6K9Q\" alt=\"許志安驚喜現身做表演嘉賓。（陳順禎 攝）\"><figcaption>許志安驚喜現身做表演嘉賓。（陳順禎 攝）</figcaption></figure><p>許志安驚喜與AK Alton型爆跳唱</p><p>其後許志安再與AK、Alton（王智德）跳唱《Rebound》，三人組合十分新鮮，期間許志安模仿美國流行天王Michael Jackson表演，擺出招牌姿勢，58歲的他狀態Fit爆，令人眼前一亮！</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127709645721702400630297.png/oxyNp3u3OEiz_L4cWv9DKKwd85arBC9DxJ78-sSe_Po\" alt=\"許志安好勁！（ViuTV電視截圖）\"><figcaption>許志安好勁！（ViuTV電視截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127709643276292096538912.png/Dq8CAOrS7kt41977G7RGLrWA2zEW4gTJFCM5eBQjOXg\" alt=\"勁！（ViuTV電視截圖）\"><figcaption>勁！（ViuTV電視截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127711800155181056734598.jpeg/-QAxSooWWAl6mPdw3LorlPfyD1Zz1Jl3MfxooDH8aKA\" alt=\"賣力跳唱。（ViuTV電視截圖）\"><figcaption>賣力跳唱。（ViuTV電視截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127711797223231488574381.jpeg/X6hlMB0EHEMtEOVFp4Pk3WJPK1XEvPeiOaBlVjmgZVY\" alt=\"賣力跳唱。（ViuTV電視截圖）\"><figcaption>賣力跳唱。（ViuTV電視截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127711793532112896248501.jpeg/8j2u-CBhzwaVn1LtgwFfSlsXDHd-AKkBdphnQHaYZ0A\" alt=\"賣力跳唱。（ViuTV電視截圖）\"><figcaption>賣力跳唱。（ViuTV電視截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127709640805715968698237.png/gHtbFXQvN1bqJzqkKIfHfZ4qHfn4Y2AFUuEbh1LhG4c\" alt=\"賣力跳唱。（ViuTV電視截圖）\"><figcaption>賣力跳唱。（ViuTV電視截圖）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127709637903126528720389.png/9-2P_KTaLzfEJsUD3E8O_wZEU9UzKg0LoHRS1KB0UtQ\" alt=\"型！（ViuTV電視截圖）\"><figcaption>型！（ViuTV電視截圖）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-03T13:09:41.057338+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":366,"images":8,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}